Introducing CloudReady

   SCROLL DOWN

Introducing CloudReady

CloudReady turns almost any computer into a Chrome device.

   Whether you’re a business, a school, or a home user, CloudReady OS is
   the fast, easy way to convert your hardware to the security and
   manageability of Google's Chrome ecosystem.
   Get started

   A Windows laptop converted to CloudReady OS, running Salesforce.com
   through the Chromium browser. A Windows laptop converted to CloudReady
   OS, running Salesforce.com through the Chromium browser.

CloudReady Introduction

   SCROLL DOWN

CloudReady Introduction

     __________________________________________________________________

An OS designed for the way you work.

   Transform your computers so they’re secure, easy to manage, and never
   slow down. CloudReady gives you all the power of the web without the
   weight or risk of traditional operating systems.
   [CloudReady+Horizontal+Logo+%281%29.png]

   It's an OS designed for now—and for what's next.

   Based on Google’s Chromium OS, the same open-source architecture as
   Chromebooks and Chrome OS, CloudReady provides unparalleled speed,
   simplicity, and security without hardware limitations, whether your
   computers are brand new or 10 years old.

   That’s why companies, non-profits, schools, and government agencies
   around the world use CloudReady to streamline and secure their devices
   when accessing web apps and VDI.
   Explore CloudReady editions & pricing


