Get CloudReady

Learn more about how CloudReady can help you.

   [ent-edition.jpg]

CloudReady for Enterprise

   Designed with security and manageability at its core, CloudReady is the
   flexible, scalable way for businesses to deploy the Chrome environment
   on almost any hardware and confidently embrace cloud resources.
   Get Started
   [edu-edition.jpg]

CloudReady for Education

   Put your school's older PCs and Macs back to work. CloudReady turns
   aging laptops and desktops into fast, secure Chrome devices that you
   can manage alongside Chromebooks in the Google Admin console.
   Get Started
   [home-edition-2.jpg]

For personal, home use

   If you’re a parent, a student, a fan, or just someone ready for a
   better OS, this is where you can install our free Home version: It has
   no tech support, no management—and no cost. (Yes, it’s really free!)
   Get the free version

