   CASE STUDY

   Building a bridge to flexible, mobile security at Tri Counties Bank

   With 79 branches and more than 1200 employees, California's Tri
   Counties Bank has found that growth means a need for flexibility when
   it comes to mobile computing for remote employees. As a financial
   institution, however, security is key.
   Read the case study to learn how Tri Counties Bank used CloudReady and
   Chrome Enterprise Upgrade to create a solution that met the bank’s
   exact specifications for how remote workers could securely and
   seamlessly access their Citrix environment from any location.
   Read the case study →
